Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 桐山也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在下到這個局面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我去年獅子王戰挑戰者淘汰賽輸的那局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然覺得很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這週末我就要去德島了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是想要從自己的敗局中找到一些東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先手6一角行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.06,0:02:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後5二步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你就要7四步是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先手只需要7四步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要把角行放在那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是喜歡在戰場上做無用的事而死的那種類型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重田先生算什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副了不起不搭理人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光在確認形式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回過神來發現自己被包圍輸掉的類型？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像關原之戰的島津軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先手6一角行 然後5二步就會很難走了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6一角行能打開局面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走角行毫無作用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接走7四步更合理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走7四步6四金的話6一角行就毫無道理了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而3五步之後7一角行更合理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果後手走5二步的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後先手走到5八飛周圍的話 更有勝算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼6一角行之後6四金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先手都沒有7四步 金將怎麼可能動得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後手走5二步的話就贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先手7四步然後4七角行怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼先手5六步怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你連這都想不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.90,0:03:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要從初段開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這招還有效吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們解開這局了就能回座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 桐山你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會6一角行 還是7四步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成這種局面開始 已經很難走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別推翻前提吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就算不上是研究了 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不當成實戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有研究的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得在變成這種局面之前做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得具體一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這樣已經不行的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噁心…之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噁心?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是覺得說得抽象一點 更有天才風範
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就隨便敷衍兩句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好說清楚 需要我幫忙刺激一下你的語言中樞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 放下我的仙人掌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是研究會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得更清楚一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為原本你都是一個人研究 所以無法好好表達吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.38,0:05:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 首先
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3七的銀還在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該說就是這裡噁心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 是怎麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先手7四步的話只會造成損失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,損失 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點我和那個小籠包意見一致
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小籠包？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出去試試嗎 正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真吵吶 閉嘴你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎…噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會看一下日程表再聯絡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 明天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 放學後沒別的事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能再來一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次就你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田這樣對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翌日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思又要你來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡了 不如說是暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴在棋盤上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山你想要喝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來吧 你想喝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 熱咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只有即溶的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再輸一局的話就無路可退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完敗什麼的 千萬要避免啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是談在故鄉比賽什麼的時候吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要勝兩局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六局是在我的故鄉吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 故鄉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山形…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼樣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了雪沒別的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不下雪的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山 河 還有田地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有田地的話就不能說一無所有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著減反政策實行 那些田現在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算跟你說這些 你也不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 漸漸變成一無所有的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人也好 田也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校也好 住家也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「正因如此才…」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他似乎想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先布個矢倉局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得昨天的棋局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就照那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8八玉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9五步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3八飛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7三桂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1六步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4二角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3七銀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5三銀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3五步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奔流而來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田先生的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同洩洪一般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之間竟有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3五角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4三步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 肩膀 還有眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細想來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣長時間地與A級棋士的思想正面交鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直如洪流一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不想隨波逐流或是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我們是職業棋士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們之間的關係 不會是單純讓另一方受惠的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田先生說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得我身上有能奪取的東西才邀請我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕只有一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得自己身上有可獻出的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才提出我想要加入研究會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像被刺中要害般地想到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有想向這個人請教的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在得到想要的東西前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會放手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:12:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天 島田先生出發前往德島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獅子王戰第三局的帷幕拉開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉強過關了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後天大家要去老鼠樂園開告別會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然我沒有被邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你為什麼要特地來告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這句話我今年說了很多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來已經是在故意欺負我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出席日也是勉強過關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有參加社團
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排名戰也止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有獲得什麼成果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 能夠晉級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是老師的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是靠老師的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說沒有成果這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊工作 一邊上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己煮飯 洗衣服 扔垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥著 賺錢 付房租
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我17歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「說不定我以後能成為大人物」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊做著這樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊只顧著去電玩店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友玩樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看電視
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來沒有擔心過房租的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃除也好 吃飯也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗衣服也好 什麼都沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再說什麼沒有成果之類的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神經大條地亂說一氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣還很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去吃點關東煮什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我請客 慶祝你順利晉級
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要去嗎 老鼠樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我們兩個大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要去？現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…還是關東煮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 就去關東煮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後 我短暫的暑假開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獅子王戰 第三局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田選手 在苦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去只能咬牙堅持 別無他法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田先生耗費的時間更多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再輸一局的話就無路可退了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完敗什麼的 千萬要避免啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請無論如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰吶?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向 還有小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我來取餐盒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿點喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該給客人喝什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的話喝茶應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但國中生和幼稚園小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該拿什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆皮壽司自然是配熱茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒巧克力嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去拿點甜食給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒可樂嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…謝謝你們的餐盒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山君 你有好好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好好吃了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過幾乎都被別人吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉強吃到了兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…放了芥末味道很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟姐姐一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女兒節那天做的 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想讓零也嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺喜歡芥末的 所以就放了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前遇到的那位 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 之前的?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心零你有沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你們好像在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說 感覺你好像單方面被罵一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心你有沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果真的是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會這樣狼狽辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不是什麼魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦 我們是姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也會吵架嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒事的 畢竟是姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃家也是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了呢 明里姐和日向姐也經常吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會嚎啕大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呢 關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是吶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 知道了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是零的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白擔心一場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們只是普通的姐弟吵架而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 日向 這樣不是更糟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看口袋松鼠老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就看口袋松鼠老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教教我 口袋松鼠老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那隻松鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說松鼠也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在同一屋簷下生活了近十年
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 那時從兩人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有散發出一絲姐弟的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎 零君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才離開了那個家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獅子王戰 第三局
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於第一百一十三手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田開 八段
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後到了五點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街上放起了令人懷念的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天第二次發現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那首曲子就是《故鄉》
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.14,0:24:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗谷名人是個怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.31,0:24:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.90,0:24:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺一直都那麼年輕 頭髮那麼旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.57,0:24:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 島田選手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.57,0:24:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天就先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.61,0:24:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.70,0:24:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三月的獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.20,0:24:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集也敬請期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口袋松鼠老師喜歡什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.33,0:24:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口香糖
